                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.6">
                        <locus from="109r">Fols 109r and following</locus>
                        <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2505Weddas#Saturday">ጸሎት፡ ወስእለት፡ ሳድሲት፡ እንተ፡
              ዘዕለተ፡ ቀዳሚት፡ ሰንበት፡ ዘአስተጋብእዋ፡ እምውዳስያት፡ እንተ፡ ዘቅብጢ፡ ወካልኣኒሆሙ።</title>
                     </msItem>
            
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i3.7">
                        <locus from="123v">Fols 123v and following</locus>
                        <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2505Weddas#Sunday">ጸሎት፡ ወስእለት፡ ሳብዓይ፡
              እንተ፡ ዘዕለተ፡ እሁድ፡ ዘአስተጋብእዋ፡ እምብዙኅ፡ ስእለታት፡</title>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
            
